{"tid":2268143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民防止許智峯被突襲DQ，遭建制派恥笑：不如防「甩轆」好過 369～","createTime":"2020-11-02T14:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T17:20:01.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b173e63de966ee02c03f13547b4c6aa6c52033","tid":2268143,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=411369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411369&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0Emt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=37462d31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D411369&h=0340467f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=411369</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】八人因五月內會的行為被控違反立法會權力及特權條例。<br />\n<br />\n當中五人是現任議員，<span class=\"red\">案件周四下午在東區裁判法院提堂，撞正立法會大會，議程之一是譴責許智峯的議案。要保住許智峯的議席，民主派原本已是「一票都不能少」，若表決時，民主派有五人到法院，議席可說是「凍過水」。</span><br />\n<br />\n主席梁君彥上周多次指出議會被無理拖延，警告會為法案審議考慮劃線。民主派擔心，梁君彥會趁此機會「落刀」。據了解，有被檢控的議員已向法庭提出改期，若不獲批淮，就計劃留守議會，即使被法庭通緝，都要確保許智峯議席安全。<br />\n<br />\n有建制派就認為是「偽命題」，因為在譴責許智峯議案前尚有一項法案，以及關於UGL事件譴責周浩鼎的議案。即使梁君彥就審議時間劃線，譴責周浩鼎的議案民主派也可以發言，<span class=\"red\">有建制派笑稱民主派與其擔心被「突襲」，不如擔心自己「甩轆」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">上周大會審議法案期間，民主黨尹兆堅要求點人數。建制齊人後，謝偉銓撤回發言，當時無民主派在會議廳阻止法案恢復二讀辯論提早結束，尹兆堅之後要向盟友道歉。</span><br />\n<br />\n有民主派表示汲取教訓，日後開會都要打醒十二分精神，不容感嘆「人類總是...」。"},{"pid":"7500bcd04a9832beb5dcf7474b27f240608d6e83","tid":2268143,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n委任派比人寸返轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4badbe24fba891d0bc7ee2b44b0ec92ce3f3a852","tid":2268143,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"249e976257c8779b082f69a27c4326a270438e46","tid":2268143,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4badbe24fba891d0bc7ee2b44b0ec92ce3f3a852","tid":2268143,"uid":231583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"7500bcd04a9832beb5dcf7474b27f240608d6e83","tid":2268143,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n委任派比人寸返轉頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"一陣又衝入嚟 ,又五毛, 又BLOCK, 又乜又物<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8815ffd5ad63a1cb30cba9973b9984619ccf84","tid":2268143,"uid":141400,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"泛民自取其辱世界第一"},{"pid":"d4964fd29acbabbfec2e7bf5629158010ef09930","tid":2268143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f8815ffd5ad63a1cb30cba9973b9984619ccf84","tid":2268143,"uid":141400,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"泛民自取其辱世界第一"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"自辱派 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaf5565e1fccea84e8a404cc18aa81c920b2d29","tid":2268143,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4964fd29acbabbfec2e7bf5629158010ef09930","tid":2268143,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f8815ffd5ad63a1cb30cba9973b9984619ccf84","tid":2268143,"uid":141400,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"泛民自取其辱世界第一"},"cite